{"tid":2062941,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"我頂唔住喇！！！！！","createTime":"2020-06-13T13:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T22:22:22.000Z","uid":123696,"like":17,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d2534ac2b285a29b45a6041d972edcb2f5642715","tid":2062941,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"好想去旅行！！！<br />\n以前因為想逃避，最癲嗰陣試過一年去9次旅行<br />\n有無連登大神可以教我點樣頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日日睇新聞已經夠絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想散吓心？銅鑼灣、尖沙咀、旺角已經晚晚行<br />\n放假連長洲、梅窩，甚至咩昂坪360都去埋<br />\n但係一返屋企、第二朝一起身，就覺得好唔開心<br />\n怕好快有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前日日睇有無平機票買<br />\n最近連平機票網都停止更新埋<br />\nFacebook已經無人貼旅行相囇命<br />\n想做一陣港豬都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以喺邊度揾返些少希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人感同身受"},{"pid":"8920ad3055564de515f562088807268f5b4bbed5","tid":2062941,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"搵lingu頂住女神幫你頂住"},{"pid":"9ca53387f3947c5b6cfa3cb7ee066cda7717d783","tid":2062941,"uid":123696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8920ad3055564de515f562088807268f5b4bbed5","tid":2062941,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"搵lingu頂住女神幫你頂住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3952cfa2d4ca07bbecef08b286df086f5ae927d","tid":2062941,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"我見香港快運有機票訂"},{"pid":"204345472fca5