":2062941,"uid":299991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2534ac2b285a29b45a6041d972edcb2f5642715","tid":2062941,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"好想去旅行！！！<br />\n以前因為想逃避，最癲嗰陣試過一年去9次旅行<br />\n有無連登大神可以教我點樣頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日日睇新聞已經夠絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想散吓心？銅鑼灣、尖沙咀、旺角已經晚晚行<br />\n放假連長洲、梅窩，甚至咩昂坪360都去埋<br />\n但係一返屋企、第二朝一起身，就覺得好唔開心<br />\n怕好快有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前日日睇有無平機票買<br />\n最近連平機票網都停止更新埋<br />\nFacebook已經無人貼旅行相囇命<br />\n想做一陣港豬都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以喺邊度揾返些少希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無人感同身受"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"搵香港的地方， 一人camp 或 野外露宿"},{"pid":"de35c8b766073d9f013e4aab40b08860c2114b4f","tid":2062941,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ca53387f3947c5b6cfa3cb7ee066cda7717d783","tid":2062941,"uid":123696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8920ad3055564de515f562088807268f5b4bbed5","tid":2062941,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"搵lingu頂住女神幫你頂住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aced1aba029e07ed0c0d42435a2389468841c93c","tid":2062941,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d18e34912535b7d1347e4ea96314f52dc1ac5872","tid":2062941,"uid":35746,"like"